name: Where In The World Is Carmen Sandiego?
description: Well this is a pretty deep cut. It relies on you remembering a not-particularly well known game from the late 1980s, and also (in the final frame) a passing knowledge of the instant-gratification bakeries of the UK. HOWEVER! As long as you're au fait with all that jazz, this comic will probably make you slightly chuckle then move on with your life. 4000 Euros please!!!!
